articles.title: Watch SpaceX launch powerful ocean-mapping satellite for Europe and NASA early Nov. 17 - Space
articles.description: Liftoff of the Sentinel-6B satellite is scheduled for 12:21 a.m. ET on Monday (Nov. 17).
